import { t } from '@superset-ui/translation';
import {
  filterNulls,
  autozoom,
  jsColumns,
  jsDataMutator,
  jsTooltip,
  jsOnclickHref,
  lineColumn,
  viewport,
  lineWidth,
  lineType,
  reverseLongLat,
  mapboxStyle,
} from './Shared_DeckGL';

export default {
  requiresTime: true,
  controlPanelSections: [
    {
      label: t('Query'),
      expanded: true,
      controlSetRows: [
        [
          lineColumn,
          {
            ...lineType,
            choices: [
              ['polyline', 'Polyline'],
              ['json', 'JSON'],
            ],
          },
        ],
        ['row_limit', filterNulls],
        ['adhoc_filters'],
      ],
    },
    {
      label: t('Map'),
      expanded: true,
      controlSetRows: [
        [mapboxStyle, viewport],
        ['color_picker', lineWidth],
        [reverseLongLat, autozoom],
      ],
    },
    {
      label: t('Advanced'),
      controlSetRows: [
        [jsColumns],
        [jsDataMutator],
        [jsTooltip],
        [jsOnclickHref],
      ],
    },
  ],
};
